Tools
=====

* [hg](http://mercurial.selenic.com/)
    * `hg diff > proj-X.Y-yourpatchname.diff`
    * `hg log -p`
* [markdown](http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/)
* [rc](http://plan9.bell-labs.com/sys/doc/rc.html)
    * [`vim` syntax file](http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2880)
    * history and file completion: `rlwrap -c -b '(){}[],+=&^%$#@"";|\' rc -l`
* [sup](http://sup.rubyforge.org/) mail client.
* usable `ed`:

        TERM=linux setterm -regtabs 2
        rlwrap ed -p '>>> ' $*

